fields.title: Kenya

fields.content: Sustainable, transparent enterprises generate jobs and income opportunities, along with the promise of hope and prosperity for farmers, families and communities.
fields.title: Changing Lives

fields.content: Strong and enduring businesses operate with respect for producers, workers and the environment.  All washing stations have been trained in a set of sustainability standards and measured against them. Standards address production and farm management, social responsibility and ethics, occupational health and safety, environmental responsibility and economic transparency.  Click here for audited results of washing station performance.
fields.title: Home Page Left

fields.content: Transparent operations build healthy businesses.   Producers become loyal cherry suppliers when they understand washing station expenses, profits and payments.  Service providers have immediate access to washing station financials, allowing for real time monitoring of investments and course correction.  Benchmarking across washing stations can identify opportunities for operational improvements and efficiencies.  Click here to review washing station financial information.
